    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who ride cycles, such as bicycles, motorcycles, tricycles, and unicycles, as well as stationary exercise cycles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
